<plot>A nameless drifter meets an enigmatic woman at the watermill during Chosun times. What follows is a tale full of most of the deadly sins. A very interesting morality tale with touches of supernaturalism. The watermill (mullaebang) was supposedly a common place for lovers' trysts in that past.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?381240</url></doc>
